        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">In Europe without Switzerland, 24.72% of the sewage sludge is disposed through municipal incineration, 17.04%  in sanitary landfill, and 58.24% in landfarming. Therefore, the PV for each disposal method is calculated based on the respective percentage of the total PV of sewage sludge generated during the wastewater treatment process
Doka G.,2021. A model for composition-specific life cycle inventories of regionalised wastewater fates, Zurich, Switzerland. http://www.doka.ch/publications.htm</productionVolumeComment>
